-- Bangladesh Garment Factory Collapse Death Toll Reaches 1,000
-- B y   A r u n   D e v n a t h
-- 2013-05-09T21:12:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-09/bangladesh-garment-factory-collapse-death-toll-reaches-1-000.html
The death toll from the collapse of
the Bangladesh garment factory building two weeks ago has risen
to 1,000, Shahnewaz Mohammad Golam Zakaria, an army captain in
control room supervising the rescue operation, said by phone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
